On Monday, she made a further step in her recovery after speaking for the first time.

Under the headline 'Lauren walks!', a post from yesterday reads: 'This morning... the physical therapist assisted Lauren walking for the first time.

'Once she got halfway there, she said "30". Not sure what she meant, [her family] asked her what that means, she replied "steps!"

'What a praise, she was counting every step she took!'

But the model faces a long period of recovery as she has already undergone several emergency surgeries on her face and shoulder.

